@startuml
actor User
participant Client
participant Browser

participant ClassifiedPostController
participant ClassifiedPostService
participant ClassifiedPostRepository

database Database

User -> Client : Click "Create Classified Post"
Client -> User : Show classified post creation form

User -> Client : Fill out form and submit
Client -> Browser : POST /api/classified\nContent-Type: application/json\nBody: ClassifiedPostCreationRequest

Browser -> ClassifiedPostController : POST /api/classified
activate ClassifiedPostController
ClassifiedPostController -> ClassifiedPostController : parse JSON -> ClassifiedPostCreationRequest
ClassifiedPostController -> ClassifiedPostService : createClassifiedPost(request)

activate ClassifiedPostService
ClassifiedPostService -> ClassifiedPostService : validate title, content, projectId, authorId, status

alt Validation fails
    ClassifiedPostService --> ClassifiedPostController : throw IllegalArgumentException
    deactivate ClassifiedPostService
    ClassifiedPostController -> ClassifiedPostController : catch IllegalArgumentException
    ClassifiedPostController --> Browser : HTTP 400 Bad Request
    deactivate ClassifiedPostController
    Browser --> Client : 400 BAD REQUEST
    Client -> User : Show validation error
end

ClassifiedPostService -> ClassifiedPostRepository : save(classifiedPost)
ClassifiedPostService -> ClassifiedPostService : notify subscribers about new post
activate ClassifiedPostRepository
ClassifiedPostRepository -> Database : INSERT INTO classified_posts

Database --> ClassifiedPostRepository : Classified post is saved
ClassifiedPostRepository --> ClassifiedPostService : return saved ClassifiedPost
deactivate ClassifiedPostRepository

ClassifiedPostService --> ClassifiedPostController : return saved ClassifiedPost
deactivate ClassifiedPostService

ClassifiedPostController --> Browser : HTTP 201 Created\nBody: saved ClassifiedPost
deactivate ClassifiedPostController

Browser --> Client : 201 Created + ClassifiedPost JSON
Client -> User : Update classified posts feed with new post

@enduml